A week ago, the deputies planned to directly determine the procedure for taking the oath in the law.
From the entrant will be released children under 18 years of age, as well as incapacitated, follows from the revised text of the amendments to the bill “On citizenship of the Russian Federation” (available to “Izvestia”), which the Committee will consider on July 11 before the second reading at its meeting.
The idea of introducing an oath when joining the citizenship of the Russian Federation instead of formally signing the documents, President Vladimir Putin supported on June 6 during a meeting with the speaker of the state Duma Vyacheslav Volodin.
